txt.en:
'White Mountain Orcs patrol the Vale! Ethring is a small village without the means to defend against large-scale attacks. 

'The Orcs will flee if their numbers dwindle. Defeating these vile creatures may help us secure the safety of the town.'

<rgb=#FF0000>This bounty can only be completed a maximum of three times.</rgb>
The village of Ethring hopes to stem the tide of Orkish invaders in the the Vale by defeating any forces lurking in the valley.
You have defeated many Orcs in Ringló Vale and the people of Ethring are grateful for your deeds.
Orcs can be found throughout Ringló Vale.\n\nDefeat Orcs in Ringló Vale.
